+### Blueprint Doc Mode (`features/blueprint/`)
+
+Blueprint is the PRD documentation system. Content is authored in `.md` files under `apps/web/src/features/blueprint/docs/` and rendered via a generic `BlueprintSection` component. See `.claude/rules/blueprint-layout-design.md` for the `.md` frontmatter schema and card delimiter syntax.
+
+**CRITICAL Layout Rules:**
+
+1. **MineCard MUST have height constraints** — Cards represent future UI panels and must reflect their intended production size. Never let document content stretch a card to arbitrary height.
+   ```tsx
+   // ✅ Card with height constraint — scrolls when content overflows
+   <MineCard title="..." className="flex-[3] min-w-0 max-h-[420px]">
+
+   // ❌ Card without height constraint — stretches to fit all content
+   <MineCard title="..." className="flex-[3] min-w-0">
+   ```
+   - Use `max-h-[Npx]` or parent container `style={{ minHeight, maxHeight }}` to enforce bounds
+   - MineCard's content area already has `overflow-y-auto` — height constraints automatically enable scrolling
+   - Row 1 cards (side-by-side): `max-h-[420px]` or similar
+   - Row 2 cards (full-width): `max-h-[280px]` or similar
+
+2. **Card layout = production layout preview** — The card grid arrangement (flex ratios, row structure) should approximate the real UI layout, not just list documentation.
+
+3. **Document density → use expandable modals** — When documentation is long, put the overview in the card body and details in `expandContent` (modal). Don't let the card body grow unbounded.
+
 ### Common Mistakes to Avoid
 
 1. ❌ Using `bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl` for cards (only for nav elements)
 2. ❌ Using dark theme text colors (`text-white/70`) in cards
 3. ❌ Missing `rounded-xl` on card containers
 4. ❌ Missing `border border-mine-border` on cards
 5. ❌ Using wrong market colors (remember: red=up, green=down in Chinese markets)
 6. ❌ Missing `shadow-sm` on elevated cards
 7. ❌ Using raw hex colors instead of semantic variables
 8. ❌ Forgetting `tabular-nums` on numeric displays
+9. ❌ Blueprint MineCard without height constraint (cards must scroll, not stretch infinitely)
 
